  provinceImage3: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c9f93ce669afe814eb478ca75f7f4a0c, type: 3}
  description: "\u0110\u1ED3ng Nai l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh thu\u1ED9c v\xF9ng \u0110\xF4ng
    Nam B\u1ED9, n\u1EB1m g\u1EA7n Th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 H\u1ED3 Ch\xED Minh. \u0110\xE2y
    l\xE0 m\u1ED9t trong nh\u1EEFng \u0111\u1ECBa ph\u01B0\u01A1ng c\xF3 n\u1EC1n
    c\xF4ng nghi\u1EC7p ph\xE1t tri\u1EC3n m\u1EA1nh v\u1EDBi nhi\u1EC1u khu c\xF4ng
    nghi\u1EC7p l\u1EDBn, \u0111\xF3ng vai tr\xF2 quan tr\u1ECDng trong kinh t\u1EBF
    khu v\u1EF1c. \u0110\u1ED3ng Nai c\xF2n c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u \u0111\u1ECBa danh n\u1ED5i
    ti\u1EBFng nh\u01B0 V\u01B0\u1EDDn qu\u1ED1c gia C\xE1t Ti\xEAn v\xE0 Khu du
    l\u1ECBch B\u1EEDu Long. Ngo\xE0i ra, t\u1EC9nh c\xF2n c\xF3 h\u1EC7 th\u1ED1ng
    s\xF4ng ng\xF2i phong ph\xFA, \u0111\u1EB7c bi\u1EC7t l\xE0 S\xF4ng \u0110\u1ED3ng
    Nai, g\xF3p ph\u1EA7n quan tr\u1ECDng trong ph\xE1t tri\u1EC3n kinh t\u1EBF v\xE0
    \u0111\u1EDDi s\u1ED1ng c\u1EE7a ng\u01B0\u1EDDi d\xE2n."
  desSatNhap: "Sau khi s\xE1p nh\u1EADp v\u1EDBi t\u1EC9nh B\xECnh Ph\u01B0\u1EDBc
    v\xE0o n\u0103m 2025, t\u1EC9nh \u0110\u1ED3ng Nai c\xF3 di\u1EC7n t\xEDch 12.737,18
    km\xB2 v\xE0 d\xE2n s\u1ED1 \u0111\u1EA1t kho\u1EA3ng 4,49 tri\u1EC7u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi,
    v\u1EDBi 95 \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh c\u1EA5p x\xE3."
